        {
            "title": "美國消費者信心指數跌至四個月低點 收入擔憂加劇",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美國消費者信心指數跌至四個月低點 收入擔憂加劇\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"601\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HICiGAaNSlMYeljGmq4TFg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwMTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/e6dcdb80-8e5a-11f0-9b7d-901464f1f08b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美國消費者信心指數跌至四個月低點 收入擔憂加劇</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B3%E5%9B%9B%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%BD%8E%E9%BB%9E-%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E6%93%94%E6%86%82%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87-142707366.html",
